document_data.Notable Ceramic Items:
*''[[Alchemy jug]]s'', enchanted ceramic jugs that generated certain types of liquids or substances.{{Cite web/Princes of the Apocalypse Online Supplement|2}}
*''[[Amulet of neutrality]]'', a small ceramic disc worn by [[Veuellus Megs]] of Ravens Bluff in the late 14{{th}} century DR.{{Cite polyhedron/146/The Magic of Ravens Bluff|16}}
*''[[Firestarter]]'', a type of small cylindrical mechanical device used to create fire, usually encased in ceramic orbs or jars.
*''[[Staff of Waterdeep]]'' had several components, each possessed special magical properties. One such component was a ceramic part that exploded in paralytic shrapnel.
*''[[Star pot]]'', grenade-type of thrown alchemical weapon – ceramic jars filled with [[liquid star]] and an ignition wick.
*''[[The Blue Heron]]'', an Ancient Nubari [[artifact]] that resembled an exquisite figurine of a [[crow]] and was maroon in color.{{Cite organized play/LC/The Search for Blue Heron|15}}
